{"id":1711103,"retrievedAt":"2026-06-09T14:06:35.593Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":99,"name":"Documentary"}],"homepage":"","id":1711103,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"17th Airborne: The Bulge to the Rhine","overview":"On Christmas Day, 1944 five young soldiers of the 17th Airborne Division entered the frozen hell of the Battle of the Bulge. This is not the story of generals or strategies. It is the story of ordinary men who faced extraordinary terror fear, loss, and the fight to stay human in the chaos of war. Through their own words, these veterans recount the cold, the killing, and the haunting memories that never left them. Their courage and trauma reveal not just the brutality of war, but the strength of the human soul when survival is the only instinct left. A deeply emotional and unflinching look at the last great battle of World War II — and the men who lived to tell its truth.","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[{"id":6028,"logo_path":null,"name":"Kenwood Productions","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","name":"United States of America"}],"release_date":"1990-05-08","revenue":0,"runtime":48,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"17th Airborne: The Bulge to the Rhine","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6273145,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"James Wallace","original_name":"James Wallace","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":2,"character":"Narrator","credit_id":"6a27547a6e375f3d85b62af4","order":0}],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":6273143,"known_for_department":"Editing","name":"David L. Bowden","original_name":"David L. Bowden","popularity":0,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"6a275445807b5b1908c2e528","department":"Editing